{"tid":1958953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「他們正在埋葬寵物小精靈」法國一名電視台記者報道中國疫情時涉種族歧視被停職！","createTime":"2020-04-05T05:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T06:31:21.000Z","uid":63113,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b84843bd5a02c816a1fefe1c52824b6fad423474","tid":1958953,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e560766ed7082b0757d7766d1e6762244301915f","tid":1958953,"uid":63113,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:35:26.000Z","msg":"法國BFM電視台一名記者，在播出中國悼念疫情中犧牲烈士和逝世民眾時，說出「他們正在埋葬寵物小精靈」的言論，惹來外界抨擊涉及種族歧視。記者說未有注意當時正在收音，說出不恰當言論，電視台與涉事記者為此道歉，並宣布這名記者被停職一星期。有報道指，寵物小精靈的主要角色比卡超是黃色的卡通人物，有人曾以比卡超來比喻黃種人。<br />\n<br />\n中國全國累計確診病例超過8.2萬宗，3300多人不治，為悼念犧牲的醫護人員和逝世民眾，全國昨日早上10時在各地默哀3分鐘。國家主席習近平率領6名中央政治局常委及國家副主席王岐山等中央領導人，在中南海懷仁堂前默哀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278834&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fpage%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1278834%26csid%3D261_367&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=99ab7298\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278834&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"914b0b1c837cc59c795a617b67d68fe60d338380","tid":1958953,"uid":106870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"車厘龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7640bdcab505122a984c0a9905c040bca9cfeca","tid":1958953,"uid":334861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:35:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1357d2c953ed6e6a80939389144d66fa901a768d","tid":1958953,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" clas